Any Questions?

  • FAQ
  • Contact us

Logo Maker

I've found a logo I'd like to purchase but I need a small modification. Can you help?

No Custom Design Changes: Our goal is to provide professional and high-quality logo designs at affordable prices. This is why we've created a fully-automated logo maker. Unfortunately we cannot provide any custom changes which needs to be done by a human designer.

Our Business and Premium package includes the raw vector files (PDF and EPS format). With some basic computer knowledge and design skills, you should be able to open these files with the right software (e.g. Illustrator or Inkscape) and apply any customizations you want. Alternatively you could give the files to an external designer in addition to your specific change requests.

Can I upload my own icon?

Unfortunately it's not possible to use your own icons at the moment.

What's included?

Can I use the logo on my website and social media channels?

You can use the logo files on your website or blog right away. The BUSINESS and PREMIUM package also includes pre-sized profile pictures and cover shot photos for most common social media channels including Facebook, Instagram, Youtube, Twitter, Pinterest and LinkedIn.

Will my logo files be ready to use for printing?

Yes, the included PNG image files can be used for simple printing cases. The optimized Vector PDF/EPS files, which are available in our BUSINESS and PREMIUM package, do not lose quality when being scaled up or down in size.

These files are usually required by printing companies to print on business cards, packing material or huge billboard signs, if necessary.

Can I make changes to my logo after the purchase?

  1. The Post-Purchase Editor enables you to make unlimited text-, color- and layout changes directly in your account. Some of our competitors are charging a monthly subscription fee for a tool like this - with Smashing Logo you have access to it forever and 100% free of charge.
  2. No Custom Design Changes: Our goal is to provide professional and high-quality logo designs at affordable prices. This is why we've created a fully-automated logo maker. Unfortunately we cannot provide any custom changes which needs to be done by a human designer.
  3. Our Business and Premium package includes the raw vector files (PDF and EPS format). With some basic computer knowledge and design skills, you should be able to open these files with the right software (e.g. Illustrator or Inkscape) and apply any customizations you want. Alternatively you could give the files to an external designer in addition to your specific change requests.

Can I get the names of the used fonts?

You will receive the names of the used fonts when you purchase the Business or Premium package.

Copyright & Pricing

Is this a one-time payment or a monthly recurring payment?

It’s a one-time payment per logo. No hidden costs, no monthly subscriptions.

Do I own my logo?

As the legal owner of your logo files, you have the full copyright and ownership of your logo as a whole. You can use the purchased logo for any commercial or non-commercial purpose without any restrictions - forever.

Please check the copyrights section within our Terms of Use for more information.

Ask us anything, we are here for you 24/7! Usually you will get a reply within 24 hours. Please make sure the email you type in is correct.
